00:57:07.750 --> 00:57:07.760
is ticking; the sand in the hourglass is running short.

00:57:07.760 --> 00:57:10.029
What will you do with this

00:57:10.039 --> 00:57:14.069
window

00:57:18.670 --> 00:57:18.680
of

00:57:26.319 --> 00:57:29.349
time?

00:58:33.079 --> 00:58:37.150
I see him standing on

00:58:37.160 --> 00:58:40.390
that podium.

00:58:40.400 --> 00:58:45.630
I see Israel

00:58:45.630 --> 00:58:45.640
and

00:58:45.640 --> 00:58:53.870
Europe.

00:58:53.870 --> 00:58:53.880
The

00:58:53.880 --> 00:58:56.710
wealth transfer

00:58:56.720 --> 00:58:59.190
for the Body is

00:58:59.200 --> 00:59:02.230
an act of

00:59:02.240 --> 00:59:06.069
grace. What will

00:59:06.069 --> 00:59:06.079
you

00:59:06.079 --> 00:59:08.510
do

00:59:08.510 --> 00:59:08.520
with

00:59:08.520 --> 00:59:11.549
it?

00:59:11.559 --> 00:59:14.349
There's

00:59:14.349 --> 00:59:14.359
a

00:59:14.359 --> 00:59:17.029
purpose

00:59:17.029 --> 00:59:17.039
for

00:59:17.039 --> 00:59:20.670
it.

00:59:20.680 --> 00:59:23.750
A great storm is coming.

00:59:57.359 --> 00:59:59.270
The Body of Christ is in a slumber

00:59:59.280 --> 01:00:02.670
across

01:00:02.680 --> 01:00:04.829
America, and there will be a great

01:00:04.839 --> 01:00:08.390
shaking to

01:00:08.400 --> 01:00:12.230
awaken.

01:00:31.000 --> 01:00:33.190
Keep your eyes vertical. The

01:00:35.599 --> 01:00:37.710
wealth

01:00:39.480 --> 01:00:41.789
transfer

01:00:56.319 --> 01:01:00.029
is an act

01:01:00.029 --> 01:01:00.039
of

01:01:00.039 --> 01:01:02.510
grace. God is

01:01:02.520 --> 01:01:05.750
able.

01:02:04.279 --> 01:02:07.510
Put a

01:02:07.520 --> 01:02:09.829
smile on your face and a song in your

01:02:09.839 --> 01:02:12.269
heart. Jesus loves you so much.

01:02:14.000 --> 01:02:17.760
God bless you all. Bye-bye.

